<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office">
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:400,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

  <style>
    * {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Raleway, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: #f9f9ff;
    }

    .wrapper {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      min-width: 400px;
      max-width: 650px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 30px 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .lock {
      text-align: center;
      width: 260px;
      height: 280px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .description {
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 20px;
    }

    .description-text {
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 20px;
    }

    .url {
      display: block;
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      outline: none;
      border: 0;
      background: #FDB441;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 10px 26px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: black;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: inline-block;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
      object-fit: cover;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .logo span {
      font-size: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: bold;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <img class="lock" src="cid:lock" alt="lock">
  <h3 class="title">Forget password ?</h3>
  <p class="description">
    Hi {{ name }}, if you've lost your password or wish to reset it, use the link below to get started:
  </p>
  <a target="_blank" class="url" href="{{ url }}">{{ url }}</a>
  <p class="description-text">
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation.
  </p>

  <a class=button href="{{ url }}" target="_blank">Reset your password</a>

</div>
<div>
  <div class="logo">
    <img src="cid:logo" alt="logo">
    <h4>OSKPLAIN</h4>
  </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
